---
title: Pepper Jam Chicken plus a Kale & Sweet Potato Jumble
description: We looked below the Mason-Dixon line for inspiration and came up with this pork tenderloin, smothered in a lush pan sauce. The key is red pepper jam, which adds a tangy, sweet-savory flavor, while sour cream adds a touch of indulgence. Joining the party is a tangle of sauteed kale with roasted sweet potatoes and red onions. With a meal so plentiful and delicious, who can resist all this Southern charm?
